front.title: Thank The Maker
front.gametext: Use 1 Force during opponent's control phase if you have a droid on the table and were drained of at least 5 Force. Draw destiny. That number of cards are randomly selected and retrieved from your Lost Pile.
front.lore: Reference to 'One Who Creates,' used by droids in an almost religious way. C-3PO used phrase upon getting a much-needed cleansing oil bath.

canceledBy: Shut Him Up Or Shut Him Down
